'''Rhan'starn''' was a [[City/Legends|city]] on the [[Bothan/Legends|Bothan]] [[Homeworld/Legends|homeworld]] of [[Bothawui/Legends|Bothawui]]. 

It was located in the southern part of the [[Planet/Legends|planet's]] eastern continent. [[Liah'starn]] was to be found to the west-northwest, [[Mesdri'starn]] to the north, [[Shevre'starn]] to the northeast and [[Sal Vhe'starn]] to the east.

